data.description: Outstanding Fine Just for You for Extra Room to Roam! 5 bedrooms 3 full baths!!!Full Brickfront conveniently located  to Airport and downtown Atlanta!!In-Law Suite type of a style set up on the main. Huge Master with aa sitting area, Great for retreating away!!!Open concept in the fitchen near the family room so that evenings can be spent closer to the family! Two car garage with ample parking space for additionl cars in the driveway, That is ALWAYS a plus!! Roof recently updated. This Home is on a Slab! Not a crawlspace!! Two Fireplaces to just enjoy the scenery and the warmth of it all!Thermopane windows. ******DO Not disturb tenants!!!!!!,  No Lockbox Appointment required with 24 to 48 hour notice ******
